PrecisSetting apart, for use and benefit of the CARRY THE KETTLE BAND, of some 65 hectares of land situated in the Rural Municipality of Indian Head No. 156, near Sintaluta, Saskatchewan, together with mines and minerals, including within the road allowance, as Carry The Kettle Nakoda First Nation Indian Reserve No. 76-3.
